Token.Abstract: Set Web Analytics Mobile Analytics, Track page views within your application.

Parameter.Name: url
Parameter.Abstract: a non-nil NSString to identify the location within your app traversed by your customers. For example: com.yourpackage.viewcontrollername

Parameter.Name: title
Parameter.Abstract: a NSString (nil if n/a) to identify the title of the location within your app traversed by your customers. For example: Screen Name

Parameter.Name: item
Parameter.Abstract: a NSString (nil if n/a) to identify an item viewed by your customer. For example: UPC-1234

Parameter.Name: search
Parameter.Abstract: a NSString (nil if n/a) to identify search terms used by your customer. For example: blue jeans.
